    },
    {
      "text": "Bikkuriman (Japanese: ビックリマン; lit. Surprise Man) is a line of wafer snacks produced by Lotte, made notable for the randomly assorted bonus stickers included inside each snack. First released in 1977, Bikkuriman (ビックリマン, lit. \"Surprise Man\") became wildly popular in Japan with the introduction of the Devil VS Angel Seal (悪魔VS天使シール, Akuma vs Tenshi Shīru) series of stickers, leading to a prolific number of media tie-ins.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "『スーパービックリマン』は1993年1月29日に発売されたスーパーファミコン用ソフトの対戦格闘ゲーム。テレビアニメ『スーパービックリマン』のゲーム作品。製作はベック。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "wikipedia_ja"
    }
